-- Spanish Towns, Regions Owe Major Builders EU5B, Expansion Says
-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 2012-03-02T06:50:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-02/spanish-towns-regions-owe-major-builders-eu5b-expansion-says.html
Spanish towns and regions owe
Madrid-based builders  Ferrovial SA (FER) ,  Actividades de Construccion
y Servicios SA  and  Fomento de Construcciones & Contratas SA 
around 5 billion euros ($6.7 billion),  Expansion  reported,
without saying how it obtained the information.  In total towns and regions owe the building industry around
7 billion euros, Expansion said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Angeline Benoit in Madrid at 
